rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Woo-hoo! Big bro's back! And
this time, he's staying for good!

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0002
rows.name: Thank you so, so much for helping us!

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0003
rows.name: I still can't believe it... Pa's really back.

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I thought he'd just be lazing about the
way he used to and everything was
going to be horrible, but I was wrong.

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0005
rows.name:
He's working as hard as he can, and
he's being really nice to us! I'm sure Ma
would be happy to see us like this now!

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Pa's still not come back after all this
time...

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0007
rows.name:
That's why from this day forth, I'm
standing in as representative Ma!

rows.label: tlk41200151_03_msg0008
rows.name:
Umm, although now that I think about
it, I guess that's kinda embarrassing!
